{"tid":1567531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜丹尼爾稱從沒在中國表演被質疑港獨台獨 内地網民鬧爆：以後也別來","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T09:23:02.000Z","uid":74065,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"09e27145df5eaf771f24df31704766c26e096dc6","tid":1567531,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:06:12.000Z","msg":"近日社會不穩，無論是香港還是内地對政治議題都非常敏感。早前一眾明星護旗手令中港兩地粉絲的爭吵更嚴重，結果近日連韓國人姜丹尼爾也陷入爭議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190913_en_daniel_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190913_en_daniel_6.jpg&h=44e61224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190913_en_daniel_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190913_en_daniel_2.jpg&h=c0ac1cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜丹尼爾最近接受了内地傳媒的訪問，最後被要求向中國粉絲說幾句話時，他就說：「雖然離（韓國）很近，但一次都未能去中國表演真的很可惜」結果有網民聽到後就提出質疑，因爲明明在Wanna One時期他曾多次到香港、台灣和澳門演出，但現在卻說一次也未去過中國，所以内地的網民就認爲他有港獨、台獨之嫌，更直斥：「以後也別來！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190913_en_daniel_5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190913_en_daniel_5.jpg&h=ca6915c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190913_en_daniel_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190913_en_daniel_1.jpg&h=4e231b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190913_en_daniel_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190913_en_daniel_3.jpg&h=0c061c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190913_en_daniel_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190913_en_daniel_4.jpg&h=06c31559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過有粉絲就為姜丹尼爾解釋，表示他在Solo出道後的確未曾到内地港澳台演出，原定8月18日的香港粉絲見面會也延期至12月，所以他的説法也不是錯誤，更加不是帶有政治意識。另外也有粉絲直接分享姜丹尼爾的官方粉絲俱樂部註冊網頁，證明官方視香港、澳門和台灣為中國的一部分，希望網民不要斷章取義。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190913_en_daniel_7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190913_en_daniel_7.jpg&h=884c12ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ca90770aab3c2ccc72d7f2ddaf252db5e6b2c0c","tid":1567531,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"153a195ef1522205c1893213683c4232e4685460","tid":1567531,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:07:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0829904ee388ad8b7c7f4f52b4fc153efd70b6d","tid":1567